<h2 id="100">1. What is plentymarkets POS?</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>plentymarkets POS (<strong>Point of Sale</strong>) is our in-house developed solution for managing till sales at your brick and mortar store. The plentymarkets POS functionalities are integrated as a component that is part of
the <a href="https://knowledge.plentymarkets.com/en/app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plentymarkets app</a>.
This manual page offers you an overview on where to find information on setting up plentymarkets POS and using its functionalities to their best.</p>
</div>
